{"tid":51283,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新同事竟然用過期starbucks現金劵做聖誕交換禮物","createTime":"2016-12-23T05:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T14:49:50.000Z","uid":36497,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e74f5161d9c705891498973cb4a5ad40722b79e","tid":51283,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"天日就放假<br />\n咁岩岩lunch就叫左爭先 大家樂返黎開個小型party<br />\n順便玩下交換禮物 抽下獎咁<br />\n<br />\n交換禮物就每人出一份100$既禮物 大家交換<br />\n<br />\n咁我就買左一對杯 60$<br />\n覺得都叫幾引<br />\n<br />\n最後我就抽中左新同事份禮物<br />\n一開，屌你老母<br />\n4張25$starbucks現金劵<br />\n但我平時唔飲咖啡 咁當蝕比佢<br />\n送比其他同事<br />\n典知同事同我講 過撚左期<br />\n我即刻問個新同事 做乜送starbuck現金劵<br />\n<br />\n佢竟然當住老細面前話因為公司部咖啡機好廢<br />\n但部咖啡機係老細買<br />\n我地當堂都o哂 黑口黑面<br />\n之後佢就扮死狗 話下年會送其他精彩d既禮物<br />\n<br />\n我地班同事即刻你眼望我眼<br />\n唔好話下年啦 過左年你仲留到係公司先講野啦<br />\n<br />\n一陣就塞哂d野比佢做 一定要玩撚死佢先得！！<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_15.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_15.gif&h=6860f8c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e37a9fc91ed13dac20a7b552941fda1e2fd8bc5e","tid":51283,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"過期野都送得出<br />\n依家d 90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47f14960988eaab515f700815e1a4adee357a4c","tid":51283,"uid":7432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"九成係90後"},{"pid":"feddc01555bcc5e05e86532c9d1d062bc59bd825","tid":51283,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好"},{"pid":"8fc38bc725d54308c97ef508872e3c14c683d371","tid":51283,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主講得好</blockquote><br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用錯ac"},{"pid":"5f3d6915ddb6d330f149fc336b4aa10e3c38cda